Latex and software for the paper

Robby McKilliam, Andre Pollok, Bill Cowley, I. Vaughan L. Clarkson and Barry Quinn, "Carrier phase and amplitude estimation for phase shift keying using pilots and data".

Run the

build.sh

bash script to compile the plots and the latex document paper.tex.  The software (and plot data) is in the /code folder.  The scripts

runsim.sh
runclt.sh

will run the simulations that generate the plots in the paper.  You require scala 2.9.x to run the simulations.